reviews.text: Travelled saturday morning  October 19th 9.04 was assisted so well by the lady in the ticket office ,advised us of prices and the best for our party. Travelling with my friend in a wheelchair the lady assisted us on the train with the ramp and rang ahead to Liverpool street to advise them we were coming. The lady was so lovely - Thank you
Great access to central London and easy access to westfield in stratford. Great for daily commute to work if you live around this area.

Enfield Lock is persistently closed on week-ends; on Sundays, closed without fail. Whoever wants to travel in to Central on the week-ends will have better luck taking a horse and carriage as Enfield Lock station will open for nobody on week-ends. Sort it out Enfield council.
